Events.RelatedDescription: Merged pull request "Consolidate generator code to aid caching" (#1353) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody: The incremental generator pipeline can cache things that don't change, but this requires anything that wants to participate to be a part of the same generator. This moves all the generation that requires the data files into a shared generator so that this can be done. One fall out of this is that the files that are generated are all in the same directory.
